snippet.title: The Whitakers Library: Part 1 - Full Playthrough (Banned Commentary)
snippet.description:
The Whitakers Library: Part 1 - Full Playthrough (Banned Commentary)

Welcome to the final days of James Whitaker's Library, where you’ve taken on what seems like a simple task: helping pack up the remnants of a once-thriving library. As the days pass, shadows grow longer, and the air fills with an unnatural chill. You soon realize that some things in this place were never meant to be disturbed. And remember, the only instructions you should follow are those from James Whitaker himself. Can you survive the mysteries lurking within?

https://lorex-games.itch.io/the-whitakers-library-part-1
